  ('Sita the Cheetah', 'Female', 'Big cats', 150, 'https://cdn.pixabay.com/photo/2022/09/07/09/29/cheetah-7438381_1280.jpg', 'Sita is very playful she is good with kids she loves to be outside and loves to run. She will need a very big yard to play in, and lots of space but other than that she is the perfect pet looking for her forever home.', true),
  ('Athena', 'Female', 'Big cats', 150, 'https://cdn.pixabay.com/photo/2014/02/27/16/09/lynx-275982_1280.jpg', 'Athena is a very calm lynx she is very good with children. Athena loves to be with people once you have a bond with her she loves to be with her owner she is housetrained but you could also leave her outside she is a very sweet girl and is looking for her forever family.', true),
