  ('Ricky', 'Male', 'Dog', 100, 'https://cdn.pixabay.com/photo/2012/10/06/04/16/siberian-husky-60046_1280.jpg', NULL, true),
  ('Spidey and Spunkey the Monkey', 'Male and Female', 'Monkey', 110, 'https://cdn.pixabay.com/photo/2022/02/14/02/39/animal-7012354_1280.jpg', 'Spidey and Spunkey are sweet siblings who were abandoned by their troop because the troop did not have enough food for them. Their mother was later captured by the zoo because she couldn''t keep up with the troop. We found them and took them in. We want them to go together to their forever home because we don''t want their hearts broken again.', true),
  ('Hunter', 'Male', 'Dog', 100, 'https://cdn.pixabay.com/photo/2022/12/11/16/26/dog-7649247_1280.jpg', 'Hunter is a sweet, very active Husky. He was named Hunter because he loves to play hide-n-seek with people and things. If you hide from him, he will surely find you. If you hide a treat he will also hunt until he finds it. If you leave your toys or socks on the floor, Hunter will hide them and later hunt them for you.', true),
  ('Leopardfur', 'Female', 'Cat', 75, 'https://cdn.pixabay.com/photo/2023/05/23/15/26/bengal-cat-8012974_1280.jpg', 'Our Bengal cat is an excellent companion; she is fully house-trained and has a fondness for children.', true),
  ('Chocolate', 'Male', 'Dog', 100, 'https://cdn.pixabay.com/photo/2015/06/11/14/24/labrador-805856_1280.jpg', 'Chocolate is a playful puppy who tends to chew on shoes, so it''s advisable to keep them out of reach. Additionally, he requires plenty of playtime to stay happy and engaged.', true),
  ('Kangy the Kangaroo', 'Female', 'Marsupial', 100, 'https://cdn.pixabay.com/photo/2022/09/16/23/51/kangaroo-7459870_1280.jpg', 'Kangy is a mini kangaroo so she will stay this size and she is a really good girl', true),
  ('Isabella', 'Female', 'Cat', 75, 'https://cdn.pixabay.com/photo/2018/03/09/02/06/cute-3210439_1280.jpg', 'Isabella, affectionately known as Izzy, is a gentle and affectionate cat we discovered on the streets, likely abandoned. She is in need of a caring family to provide her with the love and support she deserves.', true),
  ('Ginny', 'Female', 'Rabbit', 55, 'https://cdn.pixabay.com/photo/2017/04/10/12/51/hare-2218452_1280.jpg', 'Ginny is a fiesty lion head and aproximatly 6 months old and looking for her forever home she is housebroken and has lovely manners', true),
  ('Miracle', 'Female', 'Cat', 75, 'https://cdn.pixabay.com/photo/2017/09/07/17/44/siam-2726108_1280.jpg', 'We found Miracle as a kitten on the streets she was lying on her side she was in awful shape she had wounds on both of her ears and cuts all over her so we took her to the vet the veterinarian cleaned her wounds and in 3 days her cuts healed but her ears were still in terrible shape 3 more days passed and she was out but the veterinarian said she would never hear again so Miracle needs a calm home with no kids and a very loving family and home', true),
  ('Pirate', 'Male', 'Dog', 100, 'https://cdn.pixabay.com/photo/2018/05/08/01/11/dalmation-dog-3382090_1280.jpg', 'Pirate is a cute little thief he steals your house shoes because thats his favorite toy so keep them out of his reach but other then that he is really sweet and well behaved', true),
  ('Suzy', 'Female', 'Dog', 100, 'https://cdn.pixabay.com/photo/2017/02/27/20/33/puppy-2104175_1280.jpg', 'Suzy is such a sweet girl probably the sweetest her she loves everyone and is house trained', true),
