  ('Sadie', 'Female', 'Cat', 75, 'https://cdn.pixabay.com/photo/2018/03/22/23/21/cute-3252251_1280.jpg', 'Sadie is a very cute kitten and she is looking for her forever home she is very playful', true),
  ('Slither', 'Female', 'Reptiles', 45, 'https://cdn.pixabay.com/photo/2018/02/06/20/27/snake-3135638_1280.jpg', 'Slither loves to watch Harry Potter and is a fan of Nagini. Slither likes people and likes to curl up and take a nap and she has special toys because she doesn''t have good eyesight', true),
  ('Mrs. Norris', 'Female', 'Cat', 75, 'https://cdn.pixabay.com/photo/2021/12/17/19/15/pet-6877246_1280.jpg', 'Mrs. Norris is a middle-aged female cat with a spirited personality. Once she is out of sight, she disappears in an instant, moving swiftly and stealthily as she explores her surroundings. Her long fur requires weekly grooming to keep it in good condition.', true),
